high_descs: Turn right and make a right into the countertop.
Pick up the ladle from the countertop.
Turn around and make a right turn to the sink.
Place the ladle in the sink and fill the sink with water, Wash it, then pick up the ladle.
Turn around and head straight towards the wall, then hang left and go straight, then make a left turn near the diningtable.
Place the ladle in the holder at the top of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Cleaning the ladle and placing it on the diningtable holder.

high_descs: Turn right and head to the countertop on your right.
Pick the ladle from the countertop.
Turn left and head to the sink.
Put the ladle in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Turn around and head towards the dining table on your left
Place the ladle on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Place the ladle on the dining table.
